<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="102" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="3.[164,1370,736,1238]" pageId="3" pageNumber="102">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[166,514,1047,1080]" pageId="3" pageNumber="102">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not assessed on The IUCN Red List. The Xingu Silky Anteater lives in an area with substantial environmental degradation and is probably threatened with extinction. Its distribution and population status, considering recent taxonomic changes, need to be urgently evaluated.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
